data.enText: if sth perplexes you, it makes you confused or worried because you do not understand it

data.chText: 她的答复令他们困惑不解。
data.enText: They were perplexed by her response.

simple_means.memory_skill: per 自始至终 + plex 重叠，折叠 → 始终重叠 → 使复杂；迷惑

example: There was a new development that complicated the matter

tr: be a mystery or bewildering to
example: Got me--I don't know the answer!

value.def: If something perplexes you, it confuses and worries you because you do not understand it or because it causes you difficulty.

example.ex: It perplexed him because he was tackling it the wrong way.
example.tran: 由于处理不当，这个问题令他大伤脑筋。

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to fold 重叠, 折叠
rootsaffixes.title: plex, plic, ply

com 加强 + plex 重叠，折叠 → 全部重叠起来 → 复杂的
complex 复杂的 + ity 具备某种性质，状况 → 复杂性

com 加强 + plic 重叠，折叠 + ity 具备某种性质，状况 → 聚集在一起〔做事〕的关系 → 同谋关系

ex 出 + plic 重叠，折叠 + ate 做，造成，使… → 把重叠的东西理出来弄清 → 解释

ex 出 + plic 重叠，折叠 + it →〔说话〕不啰嗦的 → 直爽的
im 加以… + plic 重叠，折叠 + ate 做，造成，使… →〔说话〕加以重叠 → 暗示
